                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "I've thought about this a whole bunch, and tend to be quite ambivalent about how much it applies to software in any direct way. Design patterns, for example, clearly seem a net negative.\n\nAlexander is still extremely useful as a philosophy. Particularly "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Nature of Order",
                                "style": {
                                    "italic": true
                                }
